---

<section class="section mx-auto max-w-2xl">
  <div class="mb-12">
    <div class="text-dim">
      <span class="prompt">$</span> whoami
    </div>
    <h1 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-3xl">
      Sayan Mohsin
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-1 text-dim">
      Building AI-native systems.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="text-dim space-y-1">
    <div>
      <span class="prompt">$</span> cat links.txt
    </div>
    <div class="ml-4 space-y-0.5">
      <a href="https://github.com/sayanmohsin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        github.com/sayanmohsin
      </a>
      <br />
      <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/sayanmohsin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        linkedin.com/in/sayanmohsin
      </a>
      <br />
      <a href="mailto:sayanmohsin@outlook.com">
        sayanmohsin@outlook.com
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 text-dim space-y-1">
    <div>
      <span class="prompt">$</span> cat mission.txt
    </div>
    <div class="ml-4 space-y-0.5">
      <div>Building distributed systems with Kafka &amp; Temporal</div>
      <div>Designing AI agents that code, review, and deploy</div>
      <div>Shipping full stack: backend → frontend → infra</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
